propChildren: The content of the button group.
propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
propColor: The color of the component. It supports those theme colors that make sense for this component.
propComponent:
The component used for the root node.
Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propDisableFocusRipple: If `true`, the button keyboard focus ripple is disabled.
propDisableRipple: If `true`, the button ripple effect is disabled.
propFullWidth: If `true`, the buttons will take up the full width of its container.
propSize:
The size of the button.
`small` is equivalent to the dense button styling.
stylesRoot: Styles applied to the root element.
stylesContained: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="contained"`.
stylesOutlined: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="outlined"`.
stylesText: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="text"`.
stylesDisableElevation: Styles applied to the root element if `disableElevation={true}`.
stylesDisabled: Pseudo-class applied to child elements if `disabled={true}`.
stylesFullWidth: Styles applied to the root element if `fullWidth={true}`.
stylesVertical: Styles applied to the root element if `orientation="vertical"`.
stylesGroupedHorizontal: Styles applied to the children if `orientation="horizontal"`.
stylesGroupedVertical: Styles applied to the children if `orientation="vertical"`.
stylesGroupedText: Styles applied to the children if `variant="text"`.
stylesGroupedTextHorizontal: Styles applied to the children if `variant="text"` and `orientation="horizontal"`.
stylesGroupedTextVertical: Styles applied to the children if `variant="text"` and `orientation="vertical"`.
stylesGroupedTextPrimary: Styles applied to the children if `variant="text"` and `color="primary"`.
stylesGroupedTextSecondary: Styles applied to the children if `variant="text"` and `color="secondary"`.
stylesGroupedOutlined: Styles applied to the children if `variant="outlined"`.
stylesGroupedOutlinedHorizontal: Styles applied to the children if `variant="outlined"` and `orientation="horizontal"`.
stylesGroupedOutlinedVertical: Styles applied to the children if `variant="outlined"` and `orientation="vertical"`.
stylesGroupedOutlinedPrimary: Styles applied to the children if `variant="outlined"` and `color="primary"`.
stylesGroupedOutlinedSecondary: Styles applied to the children if `variant="outlined"` and `color="secondary"`.
stylesGroupedContained: Styles applied to the children if `variant="contained"`.
stylesGroupedContainedHorizontal: Styles applied to the children if `variant="contained"` and `orientation="horizontal"`.
stylesGroupedContainedVertical: Styles applied to the children if `variant="contained"` and `orientation="vertical"`.
